reviews.review_text: good night for Jerry ballads Nice work on this Matrix.  Really like this setlist, and some really good MIDI effects throughout from the guitar section.  Jerry gives us Row Jimmy and Standing in Set 1, then Crazy Fingers and Stella in Set 2.  Unfortunately the energy level of the band overall is somewhat low.  3.5-Star Swami rating here for the performance.
